" ------ various proxy settings -----


** Apt **
[ /etc/apt/apt.conf.d/proxy.conf, /etc/apt/apt.conf ] 

Acquire {
    HTTP::proxy "http://user:pass@proxy:port";
    HTTPS::proxy "http://user:pass@proxy:port";
}

(http://bit.ly/36u7129, http://bit.ly/2GkKkCW)


** Wget **
[ /etc/wgetrc, ~/.wgetrc ]

http_proxy = http://user:pass@proxy:port
https_proxy = http://user:pass@proxy:port
ftp_proxy = http://user:pass@proxy:port

(http://bit.ly/30YfedZ)


** Git **
# git config --global http.proxy http://user:pass@proxy:port
# git config --global https.proxy http://user:pass@proxy:port

(http://bit.ly/2uvK6GJ)


